  "text": "Successfully completed the hair asset and color system implementation for the sprite generator. Key technical achievements:\n\n1. **Anchor-based positioning system**: Fixed inconsistent positioning by making all percentage calculations relative to hair dimensions rather than mixing body/hair references\n2. **Robust color system**: Implemented data-color attribute supporting multiple specification methods (currentColor, contrast, JSON arrays)  \n3. **SVG z-order control**: Solved layering issues with proper element ordering and data-z-order attributes\n4. **JSON color palette restructure**: Moved from fragile separate arrays to object structure with named colors\n\nThe system now generates consistent sprite sheets with proper hair positioning, colors, and layering. All assets are self-contained with their configuration in data attributes.",
  "sections": [
    "Project Notes"
  ],
